 h_{n} + h_{n-1} + h_{n-2} = 2h_{n-1}+ 2h_{n-2} + h_{n-3}\leq 2h_{n-1}+ 2h_{n-2} + 2h_{n-3}\leq 2 \cdot 2 ^n = 2^{n+1}
