F_{n+1}/F_n
\frac{F_{n+1}}{F_n} = \frac{F_n + F_{n-1}}{F_n} = 1 + \frac{F_{n-1}}{F_n}
n\ge 2
\frac{F_{n+1}}{F_n} = 1 + \frac{F_{n-1}}{F_n} \le 1 + 1 = 2
